The <label> rendered by FormGroup does not have a htmlFor attribute, so inputs are not programmatically associated with their labels, breaking accessibility.  
  Fix (example for ContactForm name field):  
  Line 617:    <label htmlFor={htmlFor} className="form-label">  // added htmlFor={htmlFor}

The filter tab buttons convey selection via visual style only; without aria-pressed AT users cannot know which tab is active.  
